                                <i class="fs-4 bi-speedometer2"></i> <span class="ms-1 d-none d-sm-inline">داشبورد</span>
                            </a>
                            <ul class="collapse show nav flex-column ms-1" id="submenu1" data-bs-parent="#menu">
                                <li class="w-100">
